<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Kourtney Kardashian and her sister Kendall Jenner opened up about what dating is like in their family on a new episode of Kate Hudson's podcast, Sibling Revelry.</p>

<p>As the siblings discussed who gives the best relationship advice, the eldest of the Kardashian-Jenner children, 41, immediately selected Khloé, 36.  </p>

<p>'Khloé's is harsh, harsh advice,' she explained to the Golden Glove winner, 41, and her co-host, Oliver Hudson, during an interview at Kate's home, pre-pandemic. </p>

